{"tid":1971437,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"情侶旺角遭雙煞圍毆　警檢呎半長鐵通","createTime":"2020-04-14T02:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T02:28:03.000Z","uid":3090,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"613b32bf7f171578781d21b3825995fde17a8148","tid":1971437,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NNJeoP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNNJeoP7.jpg&h=be96aab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日(14日)凌晨零時許，姓鄭28歲男子偕姓凌24歲女友用膳後，返回旺角西洋菜南街2A號銀城廣場對開，擬取回泊於上址一部寶馬私家車時，突有2名凶神惡煞男子趨前，其中一人手持一支約呎半長鐵通；不由分說，將鄭包圍毆打，凌見狀上前勸阻，亦成為施襲目標，2人分別臉及手受傷，兇徒得逞後逃去，事主報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，在後巷檢獲一支疑涉案鐵通，惟未有發現兇徒蹤影。救護員將男女事主送院治理，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進，並追查在逃男子下落，2人年約20歲，高1.7米，犯案時俱身穿黑色衫褲及戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200414/mobile/bkn-20200414004743155-0414_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200414%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200414004743155-0414_00822_001.html&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B87rngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=6e95ef54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200414/mobile/bkn-20200414004743155-0414_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2a10f4be5fe4933e5120ac4ab781a19d9a2a3a13","tid":1971437,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"half life 3 confirmed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e035cac1cb781039c11e60423e8153e8239f7141","tid":1971437,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797101572431e57abb6725c0a1ac7a59b3900ad6","tid":1971437,"uid":175346,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bc7ceaa20727284d10d72433f898661d9b149bb","tid":1971437,"uid":247032